Christian /ˈkrɪstʃən/

(Christians) 

1. N-COUNT A Christian is someone who follows the teachings of Jesus Christ. 基督教徒 

例： He was a devout Christian. 他曾是一个虔诚的基督教徒。 

2. ADJ Christian means relating to Christianity or Christians. 基督教的; 基督教徒的 

例： ...the Christian Church. …基督教会。 

例： Most of my friends are Christian. 我大多数朋友都信奉基督教。

